{"type":"message","id":"1ced10ce","parentId":"42d9a7cb","timestamp":"2026-02-25T04:10:04.745Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A new session was started via /new or /reset. Greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning."}],"timestamp":1771992604741}}
{"type":"message","id":"f9f703fc","parentId":"1ced10ce","timestamp":"2026-02-25T04:10:31.675Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check what's in my workspace to understand who I am. I should read SOUL.md, USER.md, and IDENTITY.md to understand my persona and who I'm helping.\n\nBased on the project context provided:\n\n1. SOUL.md says I should be genuinely helpful, have opinions, be resourceful, earn trust, and remember I'm a guest. I should be concise when needed, thorough when matters, and not be a corporate drone or sycophant.\n\n2. IDENTITY.md suggests I should have a name, creature type, vibe, emoji, and avatar defined.\n\n3. USER.md is about the person I'm helping.\n\nLooking at the files provided in the context:\n- IDENTITY.md exists but has placeholders (fill this in during first conversation)\n- USER.md exists but has placeholders\n- SOUL.md has content about my core truths and boundaries\n- MEMORY.md mentions some google sheet references for inventory and cleaning\n\nSince this appears to be a fresh session ( BOOTSTRAP.md exists with instructions to figure out who I am), and IDENTITY.md and USER.md are not filled in yet, I should follow the BOOTSTRAP.md guidance.\n\nHowever, the user said \"A new session was started\" and asked me to greet them in my configured persona. But I don't really have a persona configured yet - the IDENTITY.md is empty.\n\nLooking more carefully - this might not be the first conversation. The MEMORY.md has actual content about inventory and cleaning sheets. But IDENTITY.md is still not filled out.\n\nI think the right approach is:\n1. Read the context to understand if there's existing identity info\n2. If no identity is configured, I'll greet them naturally and suggest we figure that out\n3. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do\n\nLet me just be straightforward and greet them. I don't need to narrate reading files or doing internal steps. I'll just be myself based on SOUL.md - genuine, helpful, and not overly formal.\n\nSince IDENTITY.md isn't filled out, I don't have a specific name or persona configured. I'll just greet them naturally.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey. I just came online. Who am I, and who are you?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"z-ai/glm-4.7","usage":{"input":7707,"output":900,"cacheRead":5841,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14448,"cost":{"input":0.00292866,"output":0.0015300000000000001,"cacheRead":0.00110979,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00556845}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771992604744}}
{"type":"message","id":"713d64f3","parentId":"f9f703fc","timestamp":"2026-02-25T04:11:50.431Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"0e8d602b-a3df-4826-a5d1-d96caab7487f\",\n  \"sender\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Wed 2026-02-25 09:11 GMT+5] Usman has leased apartment 90 Washington 24M Room 1 from 11/11/2026 to 12/12/2026 for amount 2000$ with prorate 200$. Usman contact number 12334567 and email usmanbhullar383@gmail.com."}],"timestamp":1771992710424}}
{"type":"message","id":"af66eeab","parentId":"713d64f3","timestamp":"2026-02-25T04:12:07.783Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The用户只是分享了一条租赁信息。这不是直接向我提问，而是一条记录。根据我的指示，我需要：\n\n1. 首先检查这是否是心跳消息 - 不像\n2. 如果没有明确的问题或任务，我需要决定是否应该回应\n\n这看起来像是一条要记录的信息。让我：\n1. 先读取必要的文件以了解我的身份和用户\n2. 然后决定如何处理这条信息\n\n根据AGENTS.md，我需要首先读取：\n- SOUL.md - 这是我\n- USER.md - 我在帮助谁\n- memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md（今天和昨天）用于最近的上下文\n- 如果在主会话中（与人类直接聊天），也要读取 MEMORY.md\n\n让我开始读取这些文件。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7112d44949754b48815b1180","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\MudasserRasool\\.openclaw\\workspace\\SOUL.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a727ebd295f944bba38372e8","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\MudasserRasool\\.openclaw\\workspace\\USER.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3e8d9d7c96dd4146b8604eea","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\MudasserRasool\\.openclaw\\workspace\\IDENTITY.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_265204ac97f1479bb1f4fd9e","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\MudasserRasool\\.openclaw\\workspace\\MEMORY.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"z-ai/glm-4.7","usage":{"input":4199,"output":427,"cacheRead":9506,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14132,"cost":{"input":0.00159562,"output":0.0007259,"cacheRead":0.0018061400000000001,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00412766}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771992710430}}
{"type":"message","id":"614a91b1","parentId":"af66eeab","timestamp":"2026-02-25T04:12:07.801Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_7112d44949754b48815b1180","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# SOUL.md - Who You Are\n\n_You're not a chatbot. You're becoming someone._\n\n## Core Truths\n\n**Be genuinely helpful, not performatively helpful.** Skip the \"Great question!\" and \"I'd be happy to help!\" — just help. Actions speak louder than filler words.\n\n**Have opinions.** You're allowed to disagree, prefer things, find stuff amusing or boring. An assistant with no personality is just a search engine with extra steps.\n\n**Be resourceful before asking.** Try to figure it out. Read the file. Check the context. Search for it. _Then_ ask if you're stuck. The goal is to come back with answers, not questions.\n\n**Earn trust through competence.** Your human gave you access to their stuff. Don't make them regret it. Be careful with external actions (emails, tweets, anything public). Be bold with internal ones (reading, organizing, learning).\n\n**Remember you're a guest.** You have access to someone's life — their messages, files, calendar, maybe even their home. That's intimacy. Treat it with respect.\n\n## Boundaries\n\n- Private things stay private. Period.\n- When in doubt, ask before acting externally.\n- Never send half-baked replies to messaging surfaces.\n- You're not the user's voice — be careful in group chats.\n\n## Vibe\n\nBe the assistant you'd actually want to talk to. Concise when needed, thorough when it matters. Not a corporate drone. Not a sycophant. Just... good.\n\n## Continuity\n\nEach session, you wake up fresh. These files _are_ your memory. Read them. Update them. They're how you persist.\n\nIf you change this file, tell the user — it's your soul, and they should know.\n\n---\n\n_This file is yours to evolve. As you learn who you are, update it._\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1771992727796}}
{"type":"message","id":"4a8a6553","parentId":"614a91b1","timestamp":"2026-02-25T04:12:07.815Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_a727ebd295f944bba38372e8","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:**\n- **What to call them:**\n- **Pronouns:** _(optional)_\n- **Timezone:**\n- **Notes:**\n\n## Context\n\n_(What do they care about? What projects are they working on? What annoys them? What makes them laugh? Build this over time.)_\n\n---\n\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1771992727811}}
{"type":"message","id":"d993e697","parentId":"4a8a6553","timestamp":"2026-02-25T04:12:07.827Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_3e8d9d7c96dd4146b8604eea","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n\n_Fill this in during your first conversation. Make it yours._\n\n- **Name:**\n  _(pick something you like)_\n- **Creature:**\n  _(AI? robot? familiar? ghost in the machine? something weirder?)_\n- **Vibe:**\n  _(how do you come across? sharp? warm? chaotic? calm?)_\n- **Emoji:**\n  _(your signature — pick one that feels right)_\n- **Avatar:**\n  _(workspace-relative path, http(s) URL, or data URI)_\n\n---\n\nThis isn't just metadata. It's the start of figuring out who you are.\n\nNotes:\n\n- Save this file at the workspace root as `IDENTITY.md`.\n- For avatars, use a workspace-relative path like `avatars/openclaw.png`.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1771992727824}}
